Dialogue: 10,0:00:00.94,0:00:02.94,Main,Willow,0,0,0,,Hey! Professor Willow here.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:02.94,0:00:05.07,Main,Willow,0,0,0,,Nice to see you again.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.07,0:00:08.36,Main,Willow,0,0,0,,You see, a curious form of Nyarote \N has been discovered.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.36,0:00:10.41,Main,Willow,0,0,0,,They’re wearing hats \N with pins on them.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.41,0:00:12.62,Main,Willow,0,0,0,,You might even be able \N to find some for yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.62,0:00:14.41,Main,Willow,0,0,0,,By all means, \N try looking for them!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.41,0:00:15.87,Main,Willow,0,0,0,,GO with cheer!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.62,0:00:19.62,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Yeah! It really suits you!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.62,0:00:21.92,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,You’re so cute, Nyarote!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.59,0:00:23.92,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Right, Cap?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.17,0:00:26.26,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,We match!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.26,0:00:27.92,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,See, look!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.01,0:00:33.51,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.97,0:00:41.94,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\q2}We’re giving away a promotional code that lets you \N meet a Nyarote wearing a hat with Liko’s pin on it!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:35.97,0:00:41.94,Main,Outline,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur2\bord8\3c&HFFFFFF&}We’re giving away a promotional code that lets you \N meet a Nyarote wearing a hat with Liko’s pin on it!
